Frater Simon Fauconer, confrater Prioris Hospitalis Sancti Johannis Jerusalem in Anglia venit et protulit breve domini Regis patens coram Justiciariis hic in hec verba. Attornies received at Pickering before Richard de Willoughby‚ Robert de Hungersord, and John de Hambury, on Monday, 6th October, 1334.
